snippet.title: Dungeons and Dragons Animated Series (Fan Game) - Download Pc and Android
snippet.description:
Download at:
https://gamejolt.com/@zvitor/games

This game is a dream project, play with Dungeons and Dragon animated series characters on a game like Capcom's King of Dragons! 

Consider become a member here at Youtube or at Patreon to help me to continue doing this and others projects:
https://www.patreon.com/zvitor/posts

---- CREDITS ----
Menu and portrait Arts: Alexandre Coelho https://twitter.com/LexSeifer
Select screen Arts: Roger Cruz https://twitter.com/rogercruzbr
Extra sprites: Felipe Ribeiro https://twitter.com/Feh_R1beiro
Game Manual: BloodCrisis (bloodcrisis@gmail.com)
Cartoon Sfxs: Zetavio Deloryan
Texts in english: Rodrigo Nobrega
Quality Control: Luciano Bullock
Advisor for Kryptonian matters: Luis Felipe
